Name: facility_name
Description: The name of the facility providing flu vaccinations.

Name: facility_id
Description: The unique identifier for the facility providing flu vaccinations.

Name: facility_type
Description: Denotes the type of facility providing flu vaccinations.

Name: street1
Description: The street address of the facility providing flu vaccinations.

Name: street2
Description: Supplementary street address information of the facility providing flu vaccinations.

Name: city
Description: The city of the facility providing flu vaccinations.

Name: state
Description: The state or province of the facility providing flu vaccinations.

Name: postal_code
Description: The postal code of the facility providing flu vaccinations.

Name: country
Description: The country of the facility providing flu vaccinations. (ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 format)

Name: latitude
Description: The latitude of the facility providing flu vaccinations. (Value in decimal degrees to an accuracy of no less than 5 decimal places)

Name: longitude
Description: The longitude of the facility providing flu vaccinations. (Value in decimal degrees to an accuracy of no less than 5 decimal places)

Name: phone
Description: A contact phone number for the facility providing flu vaccinations.

Name: contact
Description: The name of a contact person for the facility providing flu vaccinations.

Name: url
Description: A website providing additional information about the business or entity administering flu vaccinations.

Name: begin_date
Description: The date on which vaccinations begin at a specified location. (ISO 8601 format)

Name: end_date
Description: The date on which vaccinations end at a specified location. (ISO 8601 format)

Name: begin_time
Description: The local time at which vaccinations begin being dispensed at a specified location. (ISO 8601 format)

Name: end_time
Description: The local time at which vaccinations finish being dispensed at a specified location. (ISO 8601 format)

Name: eligibility
Description: Limitations on eligibility for vaccinations at a specific location.

Name: documents
Description: List of any documents or documentation that might be needed to receive vaccination. Use the pipe ('|') delimiter to separate document names if multiple documents are required.

Name: cost
Description: The cost for vaccinations at a specified location (if any).

Name: currency_code
Description: Currency code for the cost of vacations. Required if cost applies. (ISO 4217 format)

Name: notes
Description: Any other relevant information relating to the dispensing of vaccinations at a specific location.

Name: file_start_date
Description: The file provides complete and reliable schedule information for vaccinations in the period from the beginning of the file_start_date day to the end of the file_end_date day.

Name: file_end_date
Description: The file provides complete and reliable schedule information for vaccinations in the period from the beginning of the file_start_date day to the end of the file_end_date day.
